## URL Redirect Strategy (No Bitly Needed)
Using Cloudflare Worker `/go/` redirects with UTM parameters baked in.
- Clean branded URLs for ads: `paradisesurfsidesc.com/go/facebook-summer`
- Redirects to destination with UTMs: `/?utm_source=facebook&utm_medium=paid&utm_campaign=summer2026`
- Server-side click logging in Cloudflare + GA4 campaign attribution
