## Coding Conventions
- All HTML files include version comment at top
- Use semantic HTML — `<section>`, `<article>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<header>`, `<footer>`
- No inline styles except for `grid-column: 1 / -1` span overrides
- No external CSS frameworks — Tailwind, Bootstrap etc not used
- External links always use `target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"`
- All forms use Formspree for submission
- `meta name="robots" content="noindex"` on all guest pages
- Images use `loading="lazy"` except hero/above-fold images
- Accessibility: `aria-label` on interactive elements, `alt` on all images

